snippet.title: Hopping Up for It - Official trailer - Now available on Steam
snippet.description:
Find it on Steam!  https://store.steampowered.com/app/502050/Hopping_Up_for_It/
A magician has stored a rabbit in his enchanted top hat.  Inside the hat is a pocket dimension he uses for storage.  But the rabbit can smell a bag of carrots outside... help the rabbit hop out, for freedom and carrots!  As you hop ever-upwards in this challenging game, you can save any time.
Reccommended for fans of games like Getting Over It with Bennett Foddy, Only Up, and Jump King.
